{
  "id": "adv_card_yu_13_03",
  "title": "鈴村優",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――生徒会長選挙の一週間前",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "二人で作ったポスターは……好評やし……\n毎日のあいさつ運動も、みんな返してくれるし……",
      "startTime": 6.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 12.5999999523
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依ちゃん、朝も昼も、うちに付き合ってくれて\nへとへとやろ……ごめんな……",
      "startTime": 16.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 20.8333332856
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "謝らないでちょうだい、ライブの準備も順調だし……\n優こそ……無理し過ぎちゃダメよ",
      "startTime": 24.9975474932,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 28.1081404209
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "ふぅ……優はいろんな生徒に話し掛けられるように\nなったわね、目に見える成果が出ていて凄いわ",
      "startTime": 31.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.8041492621
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "うちのとこに、いろんな悩みを話しに来てくれる\nようにもなったんよ。ほんまに嬉しいわ",
      "startTime": 38.9041493098,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 43.6041512966
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "「困りごと、相談ごと、鈴村優になんでもお聞かせ\n下さい」って呼び掛けた効果ね。でも……",
      "startTime": 47.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 51.927575318
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "疲れた～～～～…………",
      "startTime": 51.927575318,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 55.6301587899
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "……行きましょうか、バスが来ちゃうわ\n今日は撮影の後はオフだし、寮でゆっくりしましょう",
      "startTime": 59.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 63.5904307842
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "せやね、一旦休まんと……\n選挙もライブも息切れしてまうわ……ふわぁ",
      "startTime": 67.2279307127,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 74.8404307842
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 74.8404307842
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "優、大丈夫？\nバスが来たわよ。すぐ乗れそうだし、頑張って",
      "startTime": 77.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 81.8983898322
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依ちゃん、お母さんみたいや……\nうち、寝たりせぇへん……大丈夫やで……",
      "startTime": 85.3983898799,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_bus-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6166.666666600008,
          "startTime": 91.5650565465
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "ねぇ、優……そういえば、生徒会長を目指す理由は\n言葉になった？　そろそろ、教えてくれると……",
      "startTime": 96.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "すぅ……すぅ……",
      "startTime": 101.10555377,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "寝てる……\nよっぽど疲れていたのね。ずっと一生懸命だったもの",
      "startTime": 112.7666631062,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "優、私ね、あなたのおかげで……\n学校でも、こんなに一生懸命になれて、嬉しいの……",
      "startTime": 121.7333262125,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03-rui010.m4a",
      "text": "優はいつも、私を支えてくれて……\nそれだけじゃなくて……新しい世界も見せてくれて……",
      "startTime": 130.3999954223,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03-rui011.m4a",
      "text": "ふぁ……ダメ、バスの揺れが心地良くて……\n…………すぅ……",
      "startTime": 141.0333328246,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――生徒会長選挙、候補者演説",
      "startTime": 145.0821078139,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolgym-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolgym-00-noon",
      "startTime": 146.8154406863
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolgym-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolgym-00-noon",
      "startTime": 146.8154406863
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolgym-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolgym-00-noon",
      "startTime": 150.9999994913
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03-rui012.m4a",
      "text": "いよいよ次が、優の演説の番よ\nこの後は投票を残すのみ……ここが決めどころね！",
      "startTime": 150.9999994913,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolgym-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolgym-00-noon",
      "startTime": 155.5083839574
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "……うちの演説な、瑠依ちゃんに一番聞いてほしいんよ\nせやから、ここで――うちの一番近くで聞いてくれる？",
      "startTime": 160.5083885827,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolgym-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolgym-00-noon",
      "startTime": 165.875050624
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03-rui013.m4a",
      "text": "もちろんよ、あなたから目を離したりしないわ\n一言も、聞き逃さないから",
      "startTime": 169.8666661579,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolgym-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolgym-00-noon",
      "startTime": 172.055979967
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03-yu009.m4a",
      "text": "うん、ほな行ってきます\nうちの想い、みんなにぶつけてくるわ！",
      "startTime": 175.1559845923,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolgymstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolgymstage-01-noon",
      "startTime": 179.722651259
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolgymstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolgymstage-01-noon",
      "startTime": 179.722651259
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03-yu010.m4a",
      "text": "芸能コース一年の鈴村優といいます\nうちは生徒会長に立候補して、今ここに立っています",
      "startTime": 185.2893179256,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolgymstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolgymstage-01-noon",
      "startTime": 190.6226395129
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03-yu011.m4a",
      "text": "立候補した理由は、この学校の先輩でもある親友が\n『学校の意味』に疑問を持っていたことがきっかけです",
      "startTime": 195.422651259,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolgym-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolgym-00-noon",
      "startTime": 200.4559774716
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolgym-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolgym-00-noon",
      "startTime": 200.4559774716
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03-rui014.m4a",
      "text": "え……優、それって……以前、私が聞いたこと……？\n学校に通うより、やるべきことがあるんじゃないかって",
      "startTime": 207.5666661579,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolgym-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolgym-00-noon",
      "startTime": 212.5568274656
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03-rui015.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんにも、メッセや電話で\n相談したりして……でも、随分前のことなのに……",
      "startTime": 215.1666661579,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolgymstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolgymstage-01-noon",
      "startTime": 221.440067164
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolgymstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolgymstage-01-noon",
      "startTime": 221.440067164
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03-yu012.m4a",
      "text": "うちは学校の意味を疑ったこともなかったんです\nなんとなく必要やと思っていたし、当然通いたかった",
      "startTime": 226.87339948,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
