    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03-yu013.m4a",
      "text": "でも、そうじゃない人もいる。意味があるのかって\n悩む人もいる。その悩みに、うちは向き合いたかった",
      "startTime": 236.27339948,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolgymstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolgymstage-01-noon",
      "startTime": 241.9067220846
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03-yu014.m4a",
      "text": "うち、学生時代は特別なものやと思うんです\nだって学生でいられるのは、たった数年だけなのに――",
      "startTime": 246.5400661467,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03-yu015.m4a",
      "text": "大勢の漫画家さんが題材にしたり、多くの作品が\n生み出されて。沢山の人が観て、読んで、共感して……",
      "startTime": 255.0400661467,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolgymstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolgymstage-01-noon",
      "startTime": 260.2400554179
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03-yu016.m4a",
      "text": "そんな特別な時間は、人生の中でそうあるもんやない\nだからうちは、学年も、コースも関係なく……",
      "startTime": 265.8400661467,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03-yu017.m4a",
      "text": "生徒みんなに、漫画みたいな、輝く青春を送ってほしい\n無駄じゃない、通って良かったって思える場所にしたい",
      "startTime": 276.2400661467,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolgymstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolgymstage-01-noon",
      "startTime": 281.0400472799
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03-yu018.m4a",
      "text": "その親友に聞かれた時には、答えられへんかったけど\n学校に、そんな意味を持たせたいんです",
      "startTime": 285.6400580087,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03-yu019.m4a",
      "text": "そのために、うちが生徒会長になったら\n誰でも、なんでも話を聞かせてほしいと思っています",
      "startTime": 292.6400580087,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolgymstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolgymstage-01-noon",
      "startTime": 297.2400472799
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03-yu020.m4a",
      "text": "友達にはちょっと話しにくいとか、相談しにくいとか\n誰に話していいか分からん時、うちに話してほしい",
      "startTime": 302.0067246753,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_03-yu021.m4a",
      "text": "あなたの学校生活の主人公は、あなたなんです\nあなたが輝くためのお手伝いをさせて下さい",
      "startTime": 311.2400580087,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolgymstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolgymstage-01-noon",
      "startTime": 314.9400472799
    },
    {
